// Sends a completed test result into HubSpot, matching the same real mechanism the website's
// own free screening form already uses (create/find a Contact by email, attach the result) --
// but as a Note on the contact rather than overwriting a single field, so a client's result
// history stays intact across multiple tests over time instead of each new one erasing the last.
//
// Scoring logic below is a direct, verified port of the app's own client-side scoring
// (bandInterpret + the per-dimension reverse-scoring sum, the Big Five percentage-based levels,
// and the PSQI's real 7-component clinical algorithm) -- extracted programmatically from the
// live app source rather than retyped by hand, and diffed against real client-side output for
// several tests before trusting it, specifically to avoid a subtly wrong recomputed score
// sitting in the CRM.

